      <textAnnotation id="sid-3A8C59A1-7B5A-447C-8417-6782579780B1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>*On going discussion on contract management for utilizing RFX UI/CWB, once it is finalized RFX UI/CWB boundary should be considered as a part of architecture.
